212
00:17:08,652 --> 00:17:09,820
I'm seeing her next week.

213
00:17:09,903 --> 00:17:14,074
Hey, seriously? For real?

214
00:17:15,117 --> 00:17:16,493
Man, you've still got it.

215
00:17:18,579 --> 00:17:20,289
