Just now, weren't you in the junkyard
where my buddies work?

220
00:18:49,837 --> 00:18:51,755
Why are you leaving without saying a word?

221
00:18:52,798 --> 00:18:54,550
Well, I…

222
00:18:56,260 --> 00:18:59,596
